room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology Covington in Covington
review: Such a great and interactive outing! We escaped TH3 C0D3 in 57:27 minutes and loved all of it! Shoutout to the “hinter” tonight and also Kelly for being so fabulous! Definitely great employees and experience! We’ll be back for all others offered!
